CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 10, 1953, pg. 11 reads: "Mr. and Mrs. Ernest Wainard Warren...in elaborate rites...Lovely Miss Harriett Ann Johnson, daughter of Mr. and Mrs. William Johnson, became the bride of Ernest Wainard Warren, brother of Mrs. Edward Johnson of Sharon, Pa., in a beautifully elaborate ceremony, Dec. 31, performed in bride's home..."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Johnson family, including bride Harriett Ann Johnson Warren, Mrs. William Johnson Jr., and Verran Johnson, posed in Johnson home
